config.script:
try:
#		-------------------------------Reset The Variables------------------
		self.session.custom.paginationCurrentPageLastRecord=0
		import math
		scriptName = "Packing Configuration: Main Screen: On Startup" 
		userID = self.session.custom.UserId
		system.perspective.print("UserID: " + str(userID))
		WoType = self.session.custom.WOType
		system.perspective.print('WorkOrder Type: '+ str(WoType))
		try:
			
			scriptName = "PackingConfiguration: Main Screen: Get CompleteWODetailsbyUserID"
			woName = self.session.custom.WoNumber
			self.custom.woNumber = woName
			WorkorderId=self.session.custom.WorkorderID
			system.perspective.print('woName :' + str(woName))
			ds=PackingAndLabelling.GetWorkOrderPackageConfigurations(WorkorderId)
			system.perspective.print('ds :' + str(ds))
			for i in ds:
				workOrderQty=i['workOrderQty']
				workOrderNumber=i['workOrderNumber']
	#--------------------------Production Qty----------------------------------------------------------------------------
				woNo=workOrderNumber
				goodQtyWO=ProductionOperatorConsole.getGoodQty(WorkorderId)
				for j in (goodQtyWO):
					total1=j.get('GoodQTY')
					completedQty=float(total1)
					
	#---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------	
#				completedQty=float(6)
				PlannedLotQty=i['PlannedLotQty']
				containerConfig=i['containerConfig']
				configurationName=i['configurationName']
				configurationName=i['configurationName']
				palletConfig=i['palletConfig']
				system.perspective.print("Pallet Config---->"+str(palletConfig))
				lotConfig=i['lotConfig']
				customerName=i['customerName']
				try:
					ContainerperPallet=float(float(palletConfig)/float(containerConfig))
#					system.perspective.print("ContainerperPallet--->"+str(ContainerperPallet))
					ContainerperPallet=int(math.floor(ContainerperPallet))
#					system.perspective.print("Floor ContainerperPallet--->"+str(ContainerperPallet))
				except:
					ContainerperPallet=0
				
				try:
					plannedPalletQty=float(float(workOrderQty)/float(palletConfig))
					plannedPalletQty=int(math.ceil(plannedPalletQty))
					system.perspective.print("plannedPalletQty-->"+str(plannedPalletQty))
					
				except:
					plannedPalletQty=0
				try:
					plannedContainerQty=float(float(workOrderQty)/float(containerConfig))
					plannedContainerQty=int(math.ceil(plannedContainerQty))
				except:
					plannedContainerQty=0
				try:
					completedContainerQty=float(float(completedQty)/float(containerConfig))
					completedContainerQty=int(math.floor(completedContainerQty))
				except:
					completedContainerQty=0
				try:
					completedPalletQty=float(float(completedQty)/float(palletConfig))
					completedPalletQty=int(math.floor(completedPalletQty))
				except:
					completedPalletQty=0
					
				PackingConfigId=i['PackingConfigId']
				completedLotQty=i['completedLotQty']
				workOrderNumber=i['workOrderNumber']
				partNumber=i['partNumber']
#				completedQty=i['completedQty']
				id=i['id']
				
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("TxtWorkOrderQty").props.text=workOrderQty
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("TxtPartNumber").props.text=partNumber
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("TxtProducedQty").props.text=completedQty
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("TxtCustomer").props.text=customerName
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("TxtConfiguration").props.text=configurationName
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer_0").getChild("Txtlotcontainer").props.text=containerConfig
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer_0").getChild("TxtContainerpallet").props.text=ContainerperPallet
				
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer_0").getChild("TxtContainer").props.text=str(completedContainerQty)+" / "+str(plannedContainerQty)
				self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer_0").getChild("Txtpallet").props.text=str(completedPalletQty)+" / "+str(plannedPalletQty)
				break
			
			self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("CoordinateContainer_0").getChild("DrpLblType").focus()
#----------------------------------------------------Pagination Code---------------------------------------------------------------------		
			self.session.custom.paginationCurrentPage=1
			Start=self.session.custom.paginationCurrentPage
			Search=''			
			self.session.custom.paginationCurrentPageLastRecord=10
			if Start>0:
				Start=Start-1
			else:
				pass
			length=self.session.custom.paginationCurrentPageLastRecord

			WorkOrderId=self.session.custom.WorkorderID
			containerData=PackingAndLabelling.GetWorkOrderPackageConfigurationsDetails(Start,length,Search,WorkOrderId)
			self.getChild("root").getChild("CoordinateContainer").getChild("tblPacking").props.data=containerData
			ds=containerData
			ds=system.dataset.toPyDataSet(ds)
			if len(ds)>0 and ds!=None:
				if len(ds)>0:
					cnt= ds[0]['recordsTotal']
					page=int(cnt/self.session.custom.paginationCurrentPageLastRecord)
					modpage=cnt%self.session.custom.paginationCurrentPageLastRecord
					if modpage>0:
						page=page+1
				self.session.custom.paginationTotalRecordPages=page	

		except:
			import sys, os
			errorMessage=scriptName  +' Exception : '+  str(sys.exc_info()[1])
			Authentication.exceptionLogger(errorMessage)
			system.perspective.print('Exception :: Local Packing nd Printing')
			exc_type, exc_obj,tb = sys.exc_info()
			errorMessage = "Error:"+ str(exc_obj)
			system.perspective.print(errorMessage)
			lineno = tb.tb_lineno
			system.perspective.print(lineno)

	except:
#		import sys, os
		system.perspective.print('Exception :: Local Packing nd Printing')
		exc_type, exc_obj,tb = sys.exc_info()
		errorMessage = "Error:"+ str(exc_obj)
		system.perspective.print(errorMessage)
		lineno = tb.tb_lineno
		system.perspective.print(lineno)

			self.getSibling("lblCurrentPage").meta.visible=0

			system.perspective.print("exceptions in Plant Data while reciving search a data= " + str(e))

			self.session.custom.paginationTotalRecordPages=0
